  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a feasibility study. Patients with acute abdominal pain who are planning to
      undergo a diagnostic laparoscopy are asked to participate in the study. The aim of the study
      is to evaluate if transgastric peritoneoscopy is feasible.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
